title: Chamestan
text: Chamestan (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Chamestān and Chomastan) is a city and capital of <a href="Chamestan%20District">Chamestan District</a> of <a href="Nur%20County">Nur County</a>, <a href="Mazandaran%20Province">Mazandaran Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 9,481, in 2,420 families.
